{"tid":282650,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇做開幼稚園有經驗既人?","createTime":"2017-06-13T14:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T04:43:30.000Z","uid":65379,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"592c3a75aa39e6b90b3974825abf4c0c4635291b","tid":282650,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:04:09.000Z","msg":"小弟有朋友想係大陸開幼稚園 <br />\n叫我幫人試下搵個有幼稚園教學經驗既人 上去攪 有冇連登巴打有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c381c935b76078371c6f645f50c86893bc700a9","tid":282650,"uid":116796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"佢本身做緊邊行架？ <br />\n點解想既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6edb573e73fc9fe2e36c37edfdff5e44edd5a57","tid":282650,"uid":99530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:07:04.000Z","msg":"大陸好似要識政府先開到？"},{"pid":"d2aa0d9e9eaa658b33c7c0270048fc481aa7c34f","tid":282650,"uid":82381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"讀個幼稚園算唔算有經驗"},{"pid":"69f5db0998c4b03c0a5677a16d867e673d9e3791","tid":282650,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢本身做緊邊行架？ <br />\n點解想既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為有大老板有個樓盤下面想開番間 <br />\n所以叫我朋友攪 聽佢講 唔止一間添"},{"pid":"c2506f52fe9b78548d53a9856adf515b26033e77","tid":282650,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸好似要識政府先開到？</blockquote><br />\n呢方面問左絕對唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb63f8b2c9f56b7acfd88b0d6a127e8bad414886","tid":282650,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀個幼稚園算唔算有經驗</blockquote><br />\n算 你覺得呢個經驗你值幾錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932aed7267af52776a694085b3b66f728e6bbf04","tid":282650,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>讀個幼稚園算唔算有經驗</blockquote><br />\n算 你覺得呢個經驗你值幾錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼年薪過百萬，佢咁幽默！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1587c9fdecfc3f32d3981c05bc54b04c74ba00b5","tid":282650,"uid":116796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"我係幼師 但無開幼稚園既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbcb4f061df278b44f0273dc9b2165131e66b9f","tid":282650,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係幼師 但無開幼稚園既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇識人 可以介紹下創業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc5ad6e801fe016c75c26566c9b421b659bc9fd","tid":282650,"uid":116796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係幼師 但無開幼稚園既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇識人 可以介紹下創業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有個同事以前番左福田開左間playgroup <br />\n近年番上黎做番幼稚園老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db0140d9038c1bdf696053c50a802447baa8348","tid":282650,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係幼師 但無開幼稚園既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇識人 可以介紹下創業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有個同事以前番左福田開左間playgroup <br />\n近年番上黎做番幼稚園老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咁上下 做管理層 都唔一定長期留係上面"},{"pid":"29aa9709f3294fc8d29e22302979148fb6e50290","tid":282650,"uid":35877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:29:00.000Z","msg":"識人係香港開緊國際幼稚園，仲要有兩三間分校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b0cd4ffd3ce6957afac82e670d9828ea86d995","tid":282650,"uid":46877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T20:34:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80888530f72d5895e1de97f66b921e1cda192e2f","tid":282650,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:53:28.000Z","msg":"搭上搭搵生意伙伴, 仲要係大陸搞生意, 免了.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfaf270b3ce8bf05addccecbf2faf9a0f68c07d","tid":282650,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T06:14:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭上搭搵生意伙伴, 仲要係大陸搞生意, 免了.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔係搭上搭 佢有叫我細細地玩一份<br />\n只係我唔想淨係比錢出去。<br />\n如果我又搭到路既話 我會玩埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56dfa494bceef78cc489870e2fdd31279569386a","tid":282650,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T06:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊學邊做ok? 我屋企人都係幼稚園老師 可以幫手</blockquote><br />\n想搵d經驗比較多既人 因為 係想打住香港教育個卓頭 所以係想搵管理層多d <br />\n唔好意思住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81aee17a4378c1aee18bd63411ff1e44fc758937","tid":282650,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識人係香港開緊國際幼稚園，仲要有兩三間分校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以介紹下嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8a7541660172f7a448bab8b501fa0848f6ec35","tid":282650,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T15:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f748f43dae9df8db562dfc520462b2fefd1c2b","tid":282650,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T15:27:08.000Z","msg":"連登=5p, 香討，babykingdom, <a href=\"http://she.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshe.com&d=J9oVfvWgaPX5x2D7PFKzrm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=7e1cf095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">she.com</a>, 奴工處"},{"pid":"3f22574945167484c4bd9d6472f49181cb7ac8b1","tid":282650,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登=5p, 香討，babykingdom, <a href=\"http://she.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshe.com&d=J9oVfvWgaPX5x2D7PFKzrm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=7e1cf095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">she.com</a>, 奴工處</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}